# Price proxy (optional)
# Without this, the app fetches Yahoo Finance directly from the browser.
# With it, all fetches go through your Cloudflare Worker (better reliability + shared edge cache).
#
# Deploy the worker:   npx wrangler deploy
# Then set this to:    https://retire-price-proxy.<your-subdomain>.workers.dev
VITE_PRICE_PROXY_URL=
